title: First Afrobeats Night at The Crocodile
story: The energy was electric. DJ Khaled was spinning Wizkid and Davido tracks, and the dance floor was packed from wall to wall.
notes: This event marked the beginning of the Seattle Afrobeats scene.

title: Wizkid's First Seattle Performance
story: When Wizkid stepped on stage at Showbox SoDo, the crowd went wild. He performed 'Ojuelegba' and 'Come Closer'.

title: Afrobeats Dance Workshop at UW
story: We organized a free dance workshop teaching Azonto and Shaku Shaku moves. Over 200 people showed up!
notes: Co-hosted by the African Student Association.

title: Burna Boy at Climate Pledge Arena
story: Burna Boy's 'Love, Damini' tour stop in Seattle was absolutely massive. The African Giant brought his full band.
notes: First Afrobeats artist to headline Climate Pledge Arena.

title: Seattle Afrobeats Festival Launch
story: The inaugural Seattle Afrobeats Festival brought together local DJs, dancers, food vendors, and artists.
